# Hyphy pipeline 

## Installation

HyPhy can be downloaded and installed via: 

git clone https://github.com/veg/hyphy.git
cd hyphy
cmake .
make install 

Further details regarding installation are available at: 

https://github.com/veg/hyphy/tree/master

## Changing aBSREL template
Note, the aBSREL.bf file (typically located in hyphy/TemplateBatchFiles/SelectionAnalyses) should be changed within the aBSREL.bf within this directory. 

## Running the aBSREL model 
The aBSREL model can then be run by 'bash absrel_fit.sh {gene_name}' 

For instance, bash absrel_fit.sh ARL14EP
